<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Bella Varelis had her heart shattered by Locky Gilbert in one of the most dramatic Bachelor finales to ever play out on the TV screens. </p>

<p>And now the brunette beauty has revealed she poured her heart out to her ex in a 'pretty angry' text message just days after last week's show aired. </p>

<p>On Monday, the 25-year-old marketing manager told former Bachelor stars, Laura Byrne and Brittany Hockley, that Locky had not contacted her after the show aired. </p>

<p>'It was a pretty angry text': Bachelor runner up Bella Varelis has revealed she sent her ex Locky Gilbert a 'pretty angry' text message two days after the finale</p>

<p>She surprised the girls on their podcast  Life Uncut by telling them she decided she text him instead. </p>

<p>'I've sent him a message, I haven't told anyone that,' she explained. </p>

<p>'I did send him a message after just to be like, I mean, it was like two days after, I was devastated, I was shattered, I was upset, I was angry. </p>

<p>'It was a pretty angry text, to be honest.</p>

<p>'I did send him a message after just to be like, I mean, it was like two days after, I was devastated, I was shattered, I was upset, I was angry,' she said on  Laura Byrne and Brittany Hockley's podcast Life Uncut </p>

<p>'The first part was like I feel like I've lost my best friend not just my boyfriend. It was a relationship for me.'</p>

<p>Elsewhere during the podcast, Bella revealed she is no longer 'in love' with Locky, but she has emotional 'moments' about him.</p>

<p>'Obviously... there are moments, when I thought on Friday  "I'm fine, I'm fine, I'm fine". Go to dinner with the girlfriends, had champagne and three minutes later I was bawling my eyes out,' she said. </p>

<p>'The first part was like I feel like I've lost my best friend not just my boyfriend. It was a relationship for me': Bella revealed the emotional words she told Locky </p>

<p>'I don't understand because I'm not in love with him anymore. I think I just genuinely thought he was in love with me and I think watching it back was a lot.</p>

<p>'It still hurts, obviously, because it just happened. This is my first Monday of the first week. I feel like I'm finally free.'</p>

<p>Bella then reiterated: 'No, I'm not in love with him anymore. It's like I wish I could just erase it from my memory and wish it never happened. But that's not going to happen.' </p>

<p>'It still hurts, obviously, because it just happened': Elsewhere during the podcast, Bella revealed she is no longer 'in love' with Locky, but she has emotional 'moments' about him</p>

<p>During last Thursday's Bachelor finale, audiences saw Locky declare his love for both Bella and Irena Srbinovska.</p>

<p>But he ended up choosing Irena.  </p>

<p>He told the Melbourne-based nurse: 'When I think about our future together, I'm, like, so excited and, like, I can't wait to just travel the world and, like, make all your dreams come true.'</p>

<p>'Irena, I'm so in love with you. And I can't wait to spend the rest of my life with you.'</p>

<p>Happy ending: During last Thursday's Bachelor finale, audiences saw Locky declare his love for both Bella and Irena Srbinovska, but he ended up choosing Irena</p>
